comments.body:
You have to escape Swig code in source files with `raw` block. For example:

```
{% raw %}
...
{% endraw %}
```

Thank you. I should add that   the following markdown codes meet my requirement in my practice.

``````
{% raw %}
```
{% extends "default.html" %}
{% block body %}
{% for key in user_info %}
    {{ key }}:{{ user_info[key] }}<br/>
{% endfor %}
{% endblock %}
```
{% endraw %}
``````

or

```
    {% raw %}
    {% extends "default.html" %}
    {% block body %}
    {% for key in user_info %}
        {{ key }}:{{ user_info[key] }}<br/>
    {% endfor %}
    {% endblock %}
    {% endraw %}
```

Here the `<br/>` will be escaped.

Try to escape your content with `raw` tag.

```
{% raw %}
content
{% endraw %}
```

